AHE's international activity is basically focused on its participation in the European Mortgage Federation (EMF), which groups together the mortgage loan entity associations in the European Union, and the AHE also participates in the European Covered Bond Council (ECBC) by representing the cedulas hipotecarias market.&#xd;
&#xd;
The Association plays a very active part in all the governing bodies and working groups of the EMF and ECBC, and is responsible at a national level for releasing news of communications and other reports edited by the EMF in matters regarding current issues which affect mortgage business at a European level. &#xd;
&#xd;
In this way, it provides Spain with increasing knowledge of the mortgage markets of the other European Union countries.
